CA CMS collaboration
TI Search for supersymmetry in events with at least one photon, missing
   transverse momentum, and large transverse event activity in
   proton-proton collisions at root s=13TeV

TI Search for a heavy composite Majorana neutrino in the final state with

CA CMS Collaboration
TI Search for dark matter produced in association with heavy-flavor quark
   pairs in proton-proton collisions at root s=13 TeV
